1","ref":"Judg.10.5","text":"And Jair died, and was buried in Camon.","year":-1209},{"id":"rec9ABz7hqgvlW9Sf","ref":"Judg.10.6","text":"And the children of Israel did evil again in the sight of the LORD, and served Baalim, and Ashtaroth, and the gods of Syria, and the gods of Zidon, and the gods of Moab, and the gods of the children of Ammon, and the gods of the Philistines, and forsook the LORD, and served not him.","year":-1187},{"id":"recCi0QxZqh4lgr4H","ref":"Judg.10.7","text":"And the anger of the LORD was hot against Israel, and he sold them into the hands of the Philistines, and into the hands of the children of Ammon.","year":-1187},{"id":"recyFdN0A5NgodHBc","ref":"Judg.10.8","text":"And that year they vexed and oppressed the children of Israel: eighteen years, all the children of Israel that were on the other side Jordan in the land of the Amorites, which is in Gilead.","year":-1187}]}
